com.planet_ink.coffee_mud.core.collections

Class RTree<T extends BoundedObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.planet_ink.coffee_mud.core.collections.RTree<T>

  • public class RTree<T extends BoundedObject>
extends java.lang.Object
    2D R-Tree implementation for Android. Uses algorithms from: http://www.sai.msu.su/~megera/postgres/gist/papers/Rstar3.pdf
    Author:
    Colonel32, cnvandev Adapted to 3d by:, Bo Zimmerman Found at: https://github.com/pruby/xppylons/blob/master/src/com/untamedears/xppylons/rtree/AABB.java (No license found)

        minChildren - Minimum children in a node. 2 <= minChildren <= maxChildren/2
        maxChildren - Maximum children in a node. Node splits at this number + 1
